GlobalPsp is a BusinessClass
    owned by workfile
    prefix is W8043

    Patterns
        disable StaticTranslations
        implements WorkFile

    Persistent Fields
        WorkFile                is UniqueID
        WorkFileSeq             is Numeric size 12
        PspCompany              is like Company 
        PspPoNumber             is like PurchaseOrder    
        PspPoRelease            is like PORelease 
        PspPoCode               is like POCode 
        PspAocCode              is like AddOnCharge
        PspInvoice              is an InvoiceNum
        PspAocRate              is like AOCRate 
        PspEntAocAmount         is like InternationalAmount
        PspCalcSprdAmt          is like InternationalAmount
        PspSpreadDiff           is like InternationalAmount
        PspSpreadMethod         is like SpreadMethod 
        PspTaxCode              is like TaxCode 
        PspDstAcctUnit          is like AccountingUnit
        PspDstAccount           is like GeneralLedgerChartAccount 
        PspDstSubAcct           is like SubAcct 
        PspTaxableFlag          is Boolean 
        PspAccrualFl            is Alpha size 1
        PspTaxAmount            is like InternationalCost
        PspAocOnPo              is Boolean 
        PspSummaryFlag          is Boolean 
        PspVendor               is like Vendor
        PspPurchFrLoc           is like VendorLocation 
        PspActivity             is like Project 

    Sets

        InsertionOrderSet
            indexed
            no duplicates
            primary
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                WorkFileSeq

    Actions

        Create is a Create Action

            Field Rules
                WorkFileSeq
                    autosequence

        Delete is a Delete Action

        DeleteAll is a Set Action
            restricted

            Parameters
                WorkFileHeader is UniqueID

            Instance Selection
                where (WorkFile = WorkFileHeader)

            Local Fields
                LWorkFileHeader is a WorkFile

            Parameter Rules
                WorkFileHeader
                    required
                    LWorkFileHeader = WorkFileHeader

            Action Rules
                Instance Rules
                    invoke Delete

                Empty Set Rules
                    invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader

                Set Rules
                    Exit Rules
                        invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader
